horilla-crm (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Horilla-CRM Debian package
  * Complete Customer Relationship Management system
  * Features include:
    - User Management with role-based access control
    - Customer & Partner Contact Management
    - Sales Pipeline with leads and opportunities tracking
    - Campaign Management and Analytics
    - Activity Tracking with calendar and communication logs
    - Reporting & Forecasting tools with dashboards
    - Real-time notifications via WebSocket
    - Multi-language support
    - Regional formatting and fiscal year configuration
  * System integration:
    - Systemd service configuration
    - Automatic database migrations
    - Static file collection
    - Log rotation support
    - Security hardening with dedicated user
  * Supports multiple database backends:
    - PostgreSQL (recommended)
    - MySQL/MariaDB
    - SQLite (development/testing)
  * Web server integration ready for Nginx/Apache
  * Redis support for WebSocket notifications

 -- Horilla CRM Team <support@horilla.com>  Wed, 11 Sep 2025 00:00:00 +0000
